&lt;p&gt;The Publishing Producer oversees game publishing projects with a specialized focus on Shooter or Anime-style Gacha games. In the pre-launch phase, you will focus on strategic project management, leveraging your deep understanding of genre trends and mechanics to drive success. Your key responsibilities include managing schedules, monitoring milestones, and identifying risks while ensuring seamless execution and clear communication across all stakeholders.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Following the launch, the role transitions into a proactive, hands-on approach to Live Ops and general game operations. You will be expected to dive deep into day-to-day management, stepping in to fill operational gaps and ensuring service stability and excellence. Working closely with cross-functional teams, you will provide genre-specific insights to support content updates and key initiatives throughout the game&#39;s lifecycle.&lt;/p&gt;
