&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bilingual Communication Bridge: Serve as the primary communication channel between global headquarters and local teams, ensuring all project documentation and strategic goals are accurately translated and aligned in both Korean and English.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactive Live Ops Management: Take a hands-on approach to daily game operations; actively monitor title performance and step in to manage operational tasks directly whenever gaps or emergencies arise to ensure service stability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data Analysis &amp;amp; Performance Reporting: Monitor and analyze key performance indicators (KPIs) and game metrics; prepare detailed reports on project outcomes and live service health to provide actionable insights for stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stakeholder Alignment: Ensure effective communication among publishing support teams, game developers, and relevant stakeholders to align project objectives, expectations, and deliverables.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Production Coordination: Partner with Production teams to coordinate project schedules, oversee progress, and proactively manage risks across multiple internal and external stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Progress Tracking: Utilize project management tools to monitor task completion, resource allocation, milestone achievements, and identify potential bottlenecks before they impact delivery.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Seamless Execution: Drive timely and scope-compliant project deliveries, maintaining a high standard of quality across all publishing initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Post-Launch &amp;amp; Lifecycle Support: Facilitate and drive post-launch initiatives, ensuring smooth transitions from development to live operations and managing ongoing content updates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Process Standardization: Develop and implement best practices for publishing production, standardizing workflows to enhance efficiency and scalability across various IPs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuous Improvement: Contribute to refining production goals and policies, fostering a culture of continuous improvement in all publishing and operational processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
